Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间位于恬静小镇里的寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周前突然被神秘地破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据警视厅的声明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因依然不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的线索是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺内的几尊遭到破坏的佛像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说两遍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以虽然不知道那一个会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会试着为自己而活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又是你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别...别看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊  救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的阿学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人救救他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别弄死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她再也不能卖淫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女的也完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找下一个猎物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起去拿书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说呀  没有办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也为我考虑下  不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号线的列车即将进站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你还往哪儿逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ总会设计一些出人意料的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们不全力应付的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有一死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚才的...傍晚的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个《米兰达·福斯特的迷》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是这个呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这本书不是你订的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樱丘圣订的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么叫你来取呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去以后  我们交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个星期就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是车站前的书店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿计  有些事最好提前讲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有不测  你帮我去拿那本书好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能答应我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  明天才能到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外按规定必须经本人核实才能给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我不是怀疑你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在给她打个电话你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想电话大概打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你不是玄野同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还这种打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句话说不清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听这口气  你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你在搞婚外恋对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野同学  你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要岔开话  到底这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了一句话说不清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那个男孩好像在哪儿见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨好像停了  我们出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再闷在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是人干的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个流浪汉就可以杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拼命要回去的是什么世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些杂碎还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不管是死是活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还站在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本  岸本她都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这些杂碎还能好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我还是第一次叫住女生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玄野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想泡我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  可是  我平时不这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...玄野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野计
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  和你的名字发音一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我叫惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的姓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我以前认识的一个\N女孩子长得一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在我的公寓里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温柔  我喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我完全一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:13:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就象神经病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道什么的话  就和大家说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...不是指我婚外恋的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能象加藤那样如鱼得水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿那边的黑球会自动打开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发给大家武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野同学  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后命令我们去杀某某星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就去消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这人有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说他想象力不错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我们必须要快点回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有骗你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样做的话  大家都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我们不是死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在我们活得好好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能看到东京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  怎么也不像死了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野同学  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先大家自我介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说自己的死因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后或许能有点头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我先来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫古田义一  50岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车站前经营一家书店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在在讨论啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追一个偷书少年被车撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找出真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你配合一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,26岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑  都29了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高中担任教师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫玄野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人用刀捅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是  因为婚外恋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫野崎大地  死因是溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年龄？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17  没有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不上学？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦龙二28岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做过很多工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是室户一  16岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一直在照顾他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是同志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然和我一样大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是事故  交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问...可以说几句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么都觉得我们是真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我几个月来都被人追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才被那个人找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被刀子捅中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拼命挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候这本书也被刺穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又不知道为什么只是这本书这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有死的话为什么会拿着这样的书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫神田美香  短大生  20岁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总结起来  交通事故2人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  3人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2人被捅死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溺死一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事故和捅死有什么奥秘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被地铁撞死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你不是天天来上学的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也料到一时半会儿是不会信的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我也是因为跳到地铁线里才...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫斋藤直纯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚满38岁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到去年还在银行工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这种话虽然难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为经济不景气工作丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠了一屁股债
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被追债  后来就跳下地铁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是死是活  总算可以安心一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼债的总不会找到这里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在心情也很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你先别高兴得太早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不错  开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野放下他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要使用暴力  玄野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是自杀了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个又一个的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾有过自杀来这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家都在想办法回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命想离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不错...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再让我听说这话  听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信不信由你们  马上惨烈的杀戮就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候在这里的人肯定有人要死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得先确认一下想活下来的人数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不想活  我也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听玄野你的话就对了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:20:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不大明白  但是他不像在说谎的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野  虽然不能完全相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为防万一  你说接下去会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  首先...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的生命已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的新生命怎么使用由我来决定\N就这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ  这回是什么星人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么  我也要把他们干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么星人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去干掉这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野星人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都如同纯洁无暇的婴儿一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便遭遇困苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要放弃，勇敢向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在雨中我的心因往事而作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤寂的我犹如一块浮冰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻我纤弱的手指吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使我记起你的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便现在一切都结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的那个吻我永不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的吻，永不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  如果不杀了那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.45,0:22:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就回不去  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  玄野星人
